chinese:
在兌換前你需要綁定手機以及完成首充禮包活動。
你在進行兌換前需要在任意遊戲中進行下注的數額。當該數額為0時，你可以按當前的兌換比例進行兌換。
你充值獲得的金幣需要3倍的下注數額，活動和充值贈送金幣需要8倍數額。
例子：當你充值100獲得150，你的下注數額為100*3+50*8=700
english:
Before redeeming you need to bind your cell phone and complete the first pack activity.
You need to bet the amount in any game before redemption. When the amount is 0, you can redeem it at the current redemption rate.
You need 3 x the bet amount for the coins you recharge, and 8 x the amount for the event and recharge bonus coins.
Example: When you recharge 100 and get 150, your bet amount is 100*3+50*8=700
spanish:
Antes de canjear necesitas vincular tu móvil y completar la actividad del primer pack.
Tienes que apostar la cantidad en cualquier juego antes de canjearlo. Cuando la cantidad sea 0, podrás canjearla al tipo de canje actual.
Necesitas 3 x la cantidad apostada para las monedas que recargas, y 8 x la cantidad para el evento y las monedas de bonificación de recarga.
Ejemplo: Cuando recargas 100 y obtienes 150, tu importe de apuesta es 100*3+50*8=700
portuguese:
Antes de resgatar, você precisa vincular seu telefone celular e concluir a atividade do primeiro pacote.
Você precisa apostar o valor em qualquer jogo antes do resgate. Quando o valor for 0, você poderá resgatá-lo com a taxa de resgate atual.
Você precisa de 3 x o valor da aposta para as moedas que recarregar e 8 x o valor para as moedas de bônus de evento e recarga.
Exemplo: Quando você recarrega 100 e recebe 150, o valor da aposta é 100*3+50*8=700
french:
Avant d'être remboursé, vous devez lier votre téléphone portable et compléter l'activité du premier pack.
Vous devez miser le montant dans n'importe quel jeu avant de l'échanger. Lorsque le montant est égal à 0, vous pouvez l'échanger au taux d'échange actuel.
Vous avez besoin de 3 x le montant de la mise pour les pièces que vous rechargez, et de 8 x le montant pour les pièces bonus d'événement et de recharge.
Exemple : Lorsque vous rechargez 100 pièces et que vous en obtenez 150, le montant de votre mise est de 100*3+50*8=700
indonesian:
Sebelum menukarkan, Anda harus mengikat ponsel Anda dan menyelesaikan aktivitas paket pertama.
Anda harus bertaruh dalam permainan apa pun sebelum penukaran. Jika jumlahnya 0, Anda dapat menukarkannya dengan harga penukaran saat ini.
Anda perlu 3 x jumlah taruhan untuk koin yang Anda isi ulang, dan 8 x jumlah untuk acara dan mengisi ulang koin bonus.
Contoh: Ketika Anda mengisi ulang 100 dan mendapatkan 150, jumlah taruhan Anda adalah 100*3+50*8=700

english: The game is all about making the decision when to jump off the rocket before it explodes.Press PLAY on the info screen to enter the moin game.The betting phase displays a countdown showing the time remoining to place a bet far the nextround and when it will begin.One bet can be set for a game round using the BET selector up tp a maximum.AUTO COLLECT allows an auto-eject value to be set for a round. This then plays the round and if the specified MULTIPUER is reached by the rocket, the astronaut will be automatically ejected.If an AUT0 COLLECT is set, the BET amount will default to the lowest BET amount until changed.clicking the COLLECT button during flight will end the bet in flight and return the win amount shown.
